“CLUB PARADISO” The iconic fine art image by @tonykellyworld celebrates the high Alpine Dolce Vita in its finest form.  Shot at the exclusive Club Paradiso members club overlooking St Moritz where the worlds of luxury and winter pursuits form a perfect harmony! This  limited edition print is a tribute to the cashmere clad jet set at their best!

To bring a piece of this Alpine magic to your home, click the link in the bio.
